# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# 🚀 1. DEPENDENCIES
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# 🔑 2. CRITICAL SECRETS (Never change or remove this part)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.env
.env*

# 🛠️ 3. HARDHAT CONTRACT BUILD OUTPUTS (Added for your project)
artifacts/
cache/
/hardhat-tooling2/artifacts/
/hardhat-tooling2/cache/

# 💻 4. NEXT.JS & PRODUCTION BUILDS
/.next/
/out/
/build

# 📊 5. TESTING & DEBUGGING
/coverage
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# ⚙️ 6. MISC & SYSTEM FILES
.DS_Store
*.pem
.vercel
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
certificates/